g.text: Here there will be an overview of thehighlighted demographic variable.Each of the demographic variables will have a histogram to show their distribution, and will change as you scroll. At the top of the map will be the scale for different measuresof Internet access, that you can switch between, and a rug plot to show the distribution for that variable.A few interesting places will be highlighted on the map, clicking on them will zoom to that area with this text changing to describe about that specificarea. At the bottom right, you can choose to see data at different levels of geographic area.
